 "introduction_text": "<div class=\"ql-editor read-mode\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Welcome to SMARTContract!</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Please use this form to register your organization or yourself as an individual for seamless contract collaboration. You'll be able to review, negotiate, and manage contracts directly within our platform.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kindly ensure that all required fields are filled out accurately, as this information will help us ensure smooth communication and effective contract handling throughout the lifecycle.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We\u2019re excited to collaborate with you on SMARTContract!</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 0, 0);\">*Note: To complete your registration please check your Email Inbox and set your password! Same will be sent to your Legal team member and Signee</span></p></div>",
